Introduction

UNIS (also written as U&iS) is an eight-member project girl group under F&F Entertainment. The group was formed from the survival show Universe Ticket.

The group will be active for 2 years and 6 months. The lineup consists of HyeonJu (cignature), Nana (PRIKIL), Gehlee, Kotoko, Yunha, Elisia, Yoona (Play With Me Club), and Seowon. They made their debut on March 27, 2024, with the mini album, WE UNIS.

The group name “U&iS” is an acronym for the phrase “U & I Story.” This signifies that both the group and their fans continue to write their story together, which began during Universe Ticket
